HEADWORD: Soppy
<hw>Sop"py</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Soaked or saturated with liquid or moisture; very wet or sloppy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

